on in the attainment of organizational goals and objectives. Moreover, for operating My SQL there is no requirement of internet connection which is one the main effectual aspect of it. Moreover, one of the main issues within A to Z is that employees are making misuse of internet services. Thus, use of MY SQL will overcome the issue in relation to misuse of internet to a great extent. In addition to this, MY SQL software offers high level security to the business unit because such cannot be accessed by unauthorized individual. Thus, MY SQL will reduce undesirable accounting and hacking related practices to the significant level. Lack of effective monitoring and review</p>

